# COMPANY TIMELINE & MILESTONES

* **Jan 2020:** Gigalogy founded in Tokyo
* **May 2020:** Released SmartAds
* **May 2021:** Alpha release of Gigalogy AI Platform (GAIP)
* **Feb 2022:** Released Doozie Token (DZT) on public blockchain
* **May 2022:** Beta release of GAIP
* **Jan 2023:** Finalist at JETRO Silicon Valley Pitch Competition
* **Feb 2023:** Released G-Core
* **May 2023:** Beta release of Maira
